createQueryRunner()
connect()
startTransaction()
query("SET LOCAL app.tenant_id = ...")
use queryRunner.manager for entity operations
commitTransaction() or rollbackTransaction()
release()
ou must call release() when finished to return the connection to the pool
 you must use SET LOCAL (rather than just SET)
 Middleware (to extract the tenant) or The Interceptor 
 does this take care of commitTransaction or rollbackTransaction and release to return
 the connection to the pool